#: lily-library.scm:1462
msgid ""
"Bisect between the integers @var{start} and @var{end}, both ends inclusive, to\n"
"find an integer @var{i} such that @code{(getter i)} is close to\n"
"@var{target-val}.  @var{getter} should be weakly increasing (in the mathematical\n"
"sense), and @var{target-val} should be between @code{(getter start)} and\n"
"@code{(getter end)} (included).  The optional keyword argument @code{mode}\n"
"specifies how the result is determined exactly.  With\n"
"@code{'last-less-than-or-equal}, which is the default, the result @var{i} is the\n"
"last @var{i} such that @code{(getter i)} is less than or equal to\n"
"@code{target-val}.  Alternatively, if @code{#:mode 'first-greater-than-or-equal}\n"
"is passed, the result is the first @var{i} such that @code{(getter i)} is\n"
"greater than or equal to @var{target-val}."
msgstr ""
"De reeks gehele getallen tussen @var{start} en @var{end} (beide\n"
"uiteinden meegerekend) in tweeën delen om een geheel getal @var{i}\n"
"te vinden zodanig dat @code{(getter i)} dicht bij @var{target-val} ligt.\n"
"@var{getter} moet (in wiskundige zin) zwak stijgend zijn,\n"
"en @var{target-val} moet tussen @code{(getter start)} en\n"
"@code{(getter end)} liggen (inbegrepen).\n"
"Het optionele trefwoordargument @code{mode} bepaalt hoe het\n"
"resultaat precies wordt berekend.\n"
"Met @code{'last-less-than-or-equal}, wat de standaardinstelling is,\n"
"is de uitkomst @var{i} de laatste @var{i} waarbij @code{(getter i)}\n"
"kleiner dan of gelijk is aan @code{target-val}.\n"
"Als daarentegen @code{#:mode 'first-greater-than-or-equal} wordt\n"
"doorgegeven, is het resultaat de eerste @var{i} waarbij\n"
"@code{(getter i)} groter is dan of gelijk is aan @var{target-val}."

